    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fold. Transform. Create Magic.  <strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> is here: a puzzle game where geometry bends to your will. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to challenge reality, one block at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/425731f3cba24a7e119c3532ad011733.poster.avif?t=1770576930\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/425731f3cba24a7e119c3532ad011733.webm?t=1770576930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/425731f3cba24a7e119c3532ad011733.mp4?t=1770576930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> is a mind-bending puzzle game in which you fold geometric blocks into mystical Magick shapes, challenging spatial reasoning and creative thinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/72f0f4edfc42324c40a51fe65cc75e75.poster.avif?t=1770576930\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/72f0f4edfc42324c40a51fe65cc75e75.webm?t=1770576930\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244150/extras/72f0f4edfc42324c40a51fe65cc75e75.mp4?t=1770576930\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine a world where simple shapes bend to your will, where logical thinking meets mystical transformation. <strong>ORIFOLDIUM</strong> challenges players to fold, manipulate, and create intricate magical configurations that will test the limits of spatial reasoning and creative imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Innovative Gameplay:</strong> Master the art of block folding to create mystical shapes</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-Bending Puzzles:</strong> 13 Progressive challenges that grow with your skills</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mesmerizing Aesthetic:</strong> Retro color palette meets magical geometric design</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle editor</strong> with Steam Workshop integration</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
